lead_paragraph: Yulia Zaripova, the Russian gold medalist in the women's 3,000-meter steeplechase at the 2012 London Olympics, was among 12 more athletes sanctioned Monday after testing positive in a reanalysis of their doping samples.

headline.print_headline: 2012 Olympic Women's Steeplechase Champ Fails Doping Retest
